text:
Ankur mere dost,
"Abe kal exam hai kya??" Yeh expression ka answer tere pass hi hota tha mere.
Baaki eco ke syllabus and exam se ek din pehle ki planning ki kaise answer ka jugaad krna hai. Wing ki bakchodiyan, and woh party toh zindagi mein humesha yaad rahegi, bahut hi mast maula hai tu bhai, and HUMESHA aisa hi rahiyo, kabhi kabhi ekdum se short packets mein teri energy nikalti rehti hai. 
Baaki I will always remember this quote by you, "A day may come when the courage of men fails, when we forsake our friends and break all bonds of fellowship, but it is not this day. This day we fight!!....."
Milte rahenge aage bhi bhai, harr saal ek baar minimum milne ka wada kiya hai WING A5 ne pura toh hoga hi woh!
Love you brother ‚ù§Ô∏è
author: Yadu  Sharma

text:

Milte hai jaldi!!

Cheers to this journey. Thanks man for being the part.
